OL,3,CMother remembers entering hospital and
OL,4,Crealising her son would never walk
OL,5,Cagain
OL,7,FA mother has recalled the moment she
OL,8,Fwalked into hospital and learned that
OL,9,Fher child would never be able to walk
OL,10,Fagain, following a devastating car
OL,11,Fcrash.
OL,13,FJulie Marks, whose son Seth is now a
OL,14,Fquadriplegic following a the
OL,15,Fcollision, described how she found her
OL,16,Fson struggling in hospital in 2022.
OL,18,FShe said: "I just saw Seth on a table,
OL,19,Fall wired up, that's what I remember.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
