OL,3,CMother remembers entering hospital and
OL,4,Crealising her son would never walk
OL,5,Cagain
OL,7,FJulie said: "There's two lives that
OL,8,Fhave been ruined here with Seth's
OL,9,Faccident.
OL,11,F"It's him, you know life changing, but
OL,12,Fthe driver, you know, his life is
OL,13,Fruined too.
OL,15,F"He's got a criminal history, he's
OL,16,Fbeen to prison and every day he sees
OL,17,FSeth, he's got that reminder, and
OL,18,Fthey're still really good friends,
OL,19,Fwhich is lovely, but he's got that
OL,20,Freminder too and his life will never
OL,21,Fbe the same."
