OL,5,Cagain
OL,7,FA fellow mother, Helen Saltern from St
OL,8,FTeath in Cornwall, is also speaking
OL,9,Fout as well, after her son was killed
OL,10,Fin a hit and run.
OL,12,FShe also believes people need to
OL,13,Fbetter understand the stark reality of
OL,14,Fdrink or drug driving.
OL,16,FDevon and Cornwall Police is also
OL,17,Fencouraging greater awareness of the
OL,18,F'fatal five' on the roads.
